<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />

  <title>INSPINIA | Login</title>

  <link href="/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" />
  <link href="/font-awesome/css/font-awesome.css" rel="stylesheet" />

  <link href="/css/animate.css" rel="stylesheet" />
  <link href="/css/style.css" rel="stylesheet" />
</head>

<div class="middle-box text-center loginscreen animated fadeInDown">
  <div>
    <div class="d-flex justify-content-center">
      <h1 class="logo-name">MORMCAMP</h1>
    </div>
    <h3>모름캠프에 오신걸 환영합니다.</h3>
    <p>로그인 후 이용해주세요.</p>
    <form class="m-t" role="form" action="/passportLogin" method="post">
      <div class="form-group">
        <input
          type="text"
          class="form-control"
          placeholder="ID"
          required=""
          name="admin_id"
        />
      </div>
      <div class="form-group">
        <input
          type="password"
          class="form-control"
          placeholder="password"
          required=""
          name="password"
        />
      </div>
      <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary block full-width m-b">
        로그인
      </button>

      <p id="resultMsg" style="color: crimson;"></p>
      <a href="#"><small>비밀번호를 잊으셨나요?</small></a>
      <p class="text-muted text-center"><small>회원이 아니신가요?</small></p>
      <a class="btn btn-sm btn-white btn-block" href="/admin/create"
        >회원가입</a
      >
    </form>
    <p class="m-t">
      <small>Inspinia we app framework base on Bootstrap 3 &copy; 2014</small>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>

<script>
  var result="<%=resultMsg%>";
  if(result!=""){
    document.getElementById("resultMsg").innerText=result;
  }
</script>